# Programming Paradigms

## Literature and Resources

- [Programming paradigm](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Programming_paradigm)
- [Clean Code: A Handbook of Agile Software Craftsmanship By Robert C. Martin](https://learning.oreilly.com/library/view/clean-code-a/9780136083238/)
- [Clean Code Fundamentals, by Robert C. Martin](https://learning.oreilly.com/videos/clean-code-fundamentals/9780134661742/)
- [Concepts, Techniques and Models of Computer Programming, by Peter Van Roy and Seif Haridi](https://mitpress.mit.edu/books/concepts-techniques-and-models-computer-programming)
- [FP vs OO: Choose Two by B. Goetz](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8GWZE2Y2O9E)
- [Classification of the principal programming paradigms](https://www.info.ucl.ac.be/~pvr/paradigms.html)
- [Understanding Programming Paradigms](http://www.janeve.me/software-programming/understanding-programming-paradigms)

